Welcome to Season Six. A new season with new wrestlers and amazing unscripted combat; a season that promises everything you have come to love and more.
Alexa Von Tess is currently ranked 5th. She has size, strength, and a signature move: "The Booty Drop". When Alexa Drops The Booty on her opponent's face, they're going nowhere.
Jennifer Dark is here for her fist official match up. This hot Hungarian has the body and determination, she only lacks the experience.
This match has many of your favorite holds: body scissors for submissions, head scissors, and plenty of face sitting and massive fingering.
title: Alexa Von Tess "The Badger" (1-0) vs Jennifer Dark "The Panther" (0-0)
